data.description: This stunning Abbeyville floor plan offers luxury, comfort, and convenience. Situated on one of the larger lots in the community, this 2 BR, 2 BA, 1770 sq. ft., ranch home, built in 2018, has numerous upgrades certain to accommodate your every need. Located just off the foyer, the private office provides a dedicated space for productivity. The open concept kitchen provides elegance with stainless steel appliances, upgraded cabinets, pull out shelves, granite counter tops, auto lit pantry and under-cabinet lighting. The primary suite features a tray ceiling, tiled bath, dual vanities, a stunning benched shower, transom window for ample natural light, walk-in closet and private watering closet. The split floor plans gives your guests a perfectly situated bedroom and guest bath. A dedicated wine storage is tucked away in the laundry room, where you can keep your collection organized and readily available for intimate gatherings or special occasions. The gas fireplace in the family room adds warmth and coziness, perfect for chilly evenings, while the sunroom offers a tranquil space to relax and soak up the natural light. Additionally, the residence is wired for sound, allowing you to enjoy your favorite tunes both indoors and outdoors. Step out onto the covered screen porch featuring retractable remote cool screens to keep bugs at bay. The extended patio, privacy fence panel and natural gas grill provides the perfect outdoor oasis for sizzling up delicious meals.The extended garage features additional storage, a utility sink and "magic stairs." These remote retractable stairs add convenience when making the journey up and down to your attic storage space. One of the standout features of this home is the abundance of green space. Whether you have a green thumb or simply appreciate the privacy it affords, you'll love the expansive outdoor area. The community keeps your grass cut and your sprinkler system ensures a lush and vibrant landscape all year round. Situated on an interior corner lot, privacy and tranquility are yours to cherish. The original owners have lovingly maintained this home, ensuring it is move-in ready for its next fortunate owner. Located within Sun City Peachtree, you'll have access to a wide range of amenities, including a private golf course, clubhouse and restaurant, a fitness center, indoor and outdoor swimming pools, walking trails, dog parks, theater, pickle ball, softball, tennis and more. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this remarkable home your own. Schedule a private viewing and embark on a new chapter of luxury living. Professional Pictures Coming 10/17/23.
